    mpegtsenc: use correct PES stream_id for AAC
    
    This adds the AAC codec to the list of audio codecs that results
    in a PES stream_id of 0xc0 (audio stream).
    
    Signed-off-by: Mans Rullgard <mans@mansr.com>

